Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest Dan Cummins from the Timesuck podcast to discuss his fascination of the research he has to conduct for his show, how fantasies such as revenge killing is a real thing, are cults still as prevalent today as they were in decades past, how COVID-19 has shown celebrities’ a**es, and the three talk about how lack of live venues could change the standup comedy world permanently.
